*   **[IUPAC name](/Chemical_nomenclature):** Methanidylidynesilanylium. Sounds like a mouthful, doesn't it? Like trying to pronounce a complex chemical equation after three too many drinks.
*   **[Preferred IUPAC name](/Preferred_IUPAC_name):** Silicon carbide. Simpler. Less pretentious. I can appreciate that.
*   **Other names:** Carborundum. Ah, the old classic. And [Moissanite](/Moissanite). Fancy. Like a cheap imitation trying to pass itself off as the real thing.

